title: Crochet accessories for head and feet
description:
In this collection of crochet patterns you will find headbands, hair scrunchies, hair bows and barrettes, snoods, tiaras, barefoot sandals, belts, lace umbrellas, fans, face masks and even a Viking or dwarven beard (with matching horned hat).
